<br>
Recently a couple melee classes in my guild have begun regularly complaining about pets pushing MOBs around.  It got to the point tonight on a Bertoxx run where the call was made to kill all pets.<br>
<br>
So I have some questions for some of you more raid oriented Mages.  Is &quot;pet push&quot; a big issue for your guild?  Do MTs have a hard time postioning or moving MOBs because of pets?  If pet push is real and it's not being imagined, will pets push if they don't bash or kick (ala Water pet)?  What's really going on?  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I'd like to go back to my guild an educate them (/sigh it's always something with pets) on how this supposed &quot;pet push&quot; works.  Hell they may be right, but as a Mage I feel the need to defend myself.<br>
<br>
 <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.san.rr.com/thegreenmile/kalamos-1hz.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=24305">My Profile</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> ~ <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eq.forgedsouls.org">Forged Souls</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wimzit>Wimzit</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 65<br> <font color=#333333>(3/6/03 7:00:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8974.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.harmonyofsouls.org/pics/hosicon_flag.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: &quot;Pet Push&quot; (tm)</span><hr size=1> they push pretty hardcore, so me and a mage in guild just set pets on opposite sides <p>Stabur 65 Deceiver<br>
