<br>
I also read somewhere on the forums here that the 62 water supposedly does not push. Although in my experience it does, it is a lot less then most other pets. Nothing a monk on the other side can't fix <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . <p>Arch Convoker Rhand Drago'Magica<br>
